### Get total revenue for user 1 for the past 30 days (default)
GET http://{{host}}/u2m/v1/revenue?userId={{userId}}
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}

### Get total revenue for user 1 for the past 7 days
GET http://{{host}}/u2m/v1/revenue?userId={{userId}}&days=7
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}

### Get total revenue for user 2 for the past 1 day
GET http://{{host}}/u2m/v1/revenue?userId={{userId}}&days=1
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}
